sql: SELECT MAX(`Percent (%) Eligible Free (K-12)`) FROM frpm WHERE `County Name` = 'Alameda'

SELECT `School Name`, `Percent (%) Eligible Free (Ages 5-17)` FROM frpm JOIN satscores ON frpm.CDSCode = satscores.cds JOIN schools ON schools.CDSCode = satscores.cds WHERE `District Type` = 'Continuation High School' AND rtype = 'S' AND `Percent (%) Eligible Free (Ages 5-17)` IS NOT NULL ORDER BY `Percent (%) Eligible Free (Ages 5-17)` ASC LIMIT 3
SELECT Zip FROM schools WHERE County = 'Fresno' AND Charter = 1
SELECT MailStreet || ' ' || MailCity || ' ' || MailState || ' ' || MailZip FROM schools WHERE CDSCode = (SELECT CDSCode FROM frpm ORDER BY `FRPM Count (K-12)` DESC LIMIT 1)
SELECT Phone FROM schools WHERE Charter = 1 AND OpenDate > '2000-01-01'
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM schools WHERE CDSCode IN (SELECT cds FROM satscores WHERE AvgScrMath < 400) AND Virtual = 'Yes'
SELECT schools.School FROM schools JOIN satscores ON schools.CDSCode = satscores.cds WHERE satscores.NumTstTakr > 500 AND (schools.Magnet = 1 OR schools.GSoffered LIKE '%Magnet%')
SELECT schools.Phone FROM schools JOIN satscores ON schools.CDSCode = satscores.cds WHERE satscores.NumTstTakr > 0 AND satscores.NumGE1500 > 0 ORDER BY satscores.NumTstTakr DESC LIMIT 1
SELECT SUM(NumTstTakr) FROM satscores WHERE cds IN (SELECT CDSCode FROM frpm ORDER BY `FRPM Count (K-12)` DESC LIMIT 1)
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM schools WHERE CDSCode IN (SELECT cds FROM satscores WHERE AvgScrMath > 560) AND FundingType = 'Charter'
SELECT frpm.`FRPM Count (Ages 5-17)` FROM frpm WHERE frpm.CDSCode = (SELECT cds FROM satscores WHERE AvgScrRead = (SELECT MAX(AvgScrRead) FROM satscores))
SELECT CDSCode FROM frpm WHERE `Enrollment (K-12)` > 500
SELECT MAX(`Percent (%) Eligible Free (Ages 5-17)`) FROM frpm WHERE CDSCode IN (SELECT cds FROM satscores WHERE PctGE1500 > 0.3 AND rtype = 'S')
SELECT schools.Phone FROM schools JOIN satscores ON schools.CDSCode = satscores.cds ORDER BY satscores.NumGE1500 / satscores.NumTstTakr DESC LIMIT 3
SELECT CDSCode, `Enrollment (Ages 5-17)` FROM frpm ORDER BY `Enrollment (Ages 5-17)` DESC LIMIT 5
SELECT dname, AVG(AvgScrRead) as avg_read FROM frpm JOIN schools ON frpm.CDSCode = schools.CDSCode WHERE StatusType = 'Active' GROUP BY dname ORDER BY avg_read DESC LIMIT 1
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM satscores WHERE cds IN (SELECT CDSCode FROM schools WHERE County = 'Alameda') AND NumTstTakr < 100
SELECT CharterNum FROM schools WHERE CDSCode = (SELECT cds FROM satscores WHERE AvgScrWrite = 499)
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM schools s, satscores ss WHERE s.CDSCode = ss.cds AND s.County = 'Contra Costa' AND s.FundingType = 'Directly funded' AND ss.NumTstTakr <= 250
SELECT schools.Phone FROM schools JOIN satscores ON schools.CDSCode = satscores.cds WHERE satscores.AvgScrMath = (SELECT MAX(AvgScrMath) FROM satscores)
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM frpm WHERE County Name = 'Amador' AND `Low Grade` = 9 AND `High Grade` = 12
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM frpm WHERE `County Name` = 'Los Angeles' AND `Free Meal Count (K-12)` > 500 AND `Free Meal Count (K-12)` < 700
SELECT School FROM satscores JOIN schools ON satscores.cds = schools.CDSCode WHERE County = 'Contra Costa' ORDER BY NumTstTakr DESC LIMIT 1
SELECT schools.School, schools.Street, schools.City, schools.Zip FROM schools JOIN frpm ON schools.CDSCode = frpm.CDSCode WHERE frpm.Enrollment (K-12) - frpm.Enrollment (Ages 5-17) > 30

SELECT schools.School FROM schools, frpm, satscores WHERE schools.CDSCode = frpm.CDSCode AND schools.CDSCode = satscores.cds AND frpm.`Percent (%) Eligible Free (K-12)` > 0.1 AND satscores.NumGE1500 >= 1

SELECT schools.School, schools.FundingType FROM schools JOIN satscores ON schools.CDSCode = satscores.cds WHERE schools.City = 'Riverside' AND schools.SchoolType = 'Elementary' AND satscores.AvgScrMath > 400
SELECT School, Street, City, State, Zip FROM schools WHERE County = 'Monterey' AND School Type = 'High' AND `Free Meal Count (Ages 5-17)` > 800 AND enroll12 > 0

SELECT schools.School, satscores.AvgScrWrite, schools.Phone FROM schools JOIN satscores ON schools.CDSCode = satscores.cds WHERE schools.OpenDate > '1991-01-01' AND schools.ClosedDate < '2000-01-01' AND satscores.AvgScrWrite IS NOT NULL
SELECT OpenDate FROM schools WHERE CDSCode = (SELECT cds FROM satscores ORDER BY enroll12 DESC LIMIT 1)
SELECT City, SUM(enroll12) AS total_enrollment FROM schools GROUP BY City ORDER BY total_enrollment ASC LIMIT 5

SELECT `Percent (%) Eligible Free (K-12)` FROM frpm WHERE CDSCode IN (SELECT cds FROM satscores WHERE enroll12 IN (SELECT enroll12 FROM satscores ORDER BY enroll12 DESC LIMIT 11) ORDER BY enroll12 DESC LIMIT 2)
SELECT AVG(`Percent (%) Eligible Free (K-12)`) FROM frpm WHERE `School Type` = '1-12' AND `Charter School (Y/N)` = 1 ORDER BY `Free Meal Count (K-12)` DESC LIMIT 5
SELECT schools.`School Name`, schools.Website FROM schools JOIN frpm ON schools.CDSCode = frpm.CDSCode WHERE frpm.`Free Meal Count (Ages 5-17)` BETWEEN 1900 AND 2000
SELECT Percent (%) Eligible Free (Ages 5-17) FROM frpm WHERE School Name = 'Kacey Gibson'
SELECT AdmEmail1 FROM schools WHERE Charter = 1 AND enroll12 = (SELECT MIN(enroll12) FROM schools WHERE Charter = 1)
SELECT AdmFName1 || ' ' || AdmLName1 FROM schools WHERE CDSCode = (SELECT cds FROM satscores WHERE NumTstTakr = (SELECT MAX(NumTstTakr) FROM satscores WHERE NumGE1500 IS NOT NULL))

SELECT schools.Street, schools.City, schools.Zip, schools.State FROM schools JOIN frpm ON schools.CDSCode = frpm.CDSCode JOIN satscores ON schools.CDSCode = satscores.cds ORDER BY frpm.`Percent (%) Eligible FRPM (K-12)` ASC LIMIT 1
SELECT Website FROM schools WHERE County = 'Los Angeles County' AND NumTstTakr BETWEEN 2000 AND 3000
SELECT AVG(NumTstTakr) FROM satscores WHERE cds IN (SELECT CDSCode FROM schools WHERE City = 'Fresno' AND OpenDate BETWEEN '1/1/1980' AND '12/31/1980')
SELECT schools.Phone FROM schools JOIN satscores ON schools.CDSCode = satscores.cds WHERE schools.District = 'Fresno Unified' ORDER BY satscores.AvgScrRead ASC LIMIT 1

SELECT schools.School, satscores.AvgScrRead FROM schools JOIN satscores ON schools.CDSCode = satscores.cds WHERE schools.Virtual = 'Yes' AND satscores.AvgScrRead IS NOT NULL ORDER BY satscores.AvgScrRead DESC LIMIT 5
SELECT s.EdOpsName FROM schools s JOIN satscores ss ON s.CDSCode = ss.cds WHERE ss.AvgScrMath = (SELECT MAX(AvgScrMath) FROM satscores WHERE rtype = 'S')

SELECT AVG(AvgScrMath), County FROM satscores JOIN schools ON satscores.cds = schools.CDSCode WHERE satscores.AvgScrRead + satscores.AvgScrMath + satscores.AvgScrWrite = (SELECT MIN(AvgScrRead + AvgScrMath + AvgScrWrite) FROM satscores) GROUP BY County

SELECT AVG(AvgScrWrite), schools.City FROM satscores JOIN schools ON satscores.cds = schools.CDSCode WHERE satscores.NumGE1500 > 0 AND satscores.NumTstTakr = (SELECT MAX(NumTstTakr) FROM satscores WHERE NumGE1500 > 0) GROUP BY schools.City

SELECT schools.School, AVG(satscores.AvgScrRead) AS AvgReadingScore FROM schools JOIN satscores ON schools.CDSCode = satscores.cds WHERE schools.AdmLName1 = 'Ulrich' GROUP BY schools.School ORDER BY AvgReadingScore DESC

SELECT schools.State, SUM(frpm.`Enrollment (K-12)`) AS enrollees FROM schools JOIN frpm ON schools.CDSCode = frpm.CDSCode WHERE schools.StatusType = 'Active' AND schools.GSoffered = 'Special Education' AND frpm.`Low Grade` = '1' AND frpm.`High Grade` = '12' GROUP BY schools.State ORDER BY enrollees DESC
SELECT AVG(1.0) FROM schools WHERE County = 'Alameda County' AND District = 'Elementary School District' AND OpenDate like '1980-%'

SELECT COUNT(*) FROM schools WHERE County = 'Orange' AND District = 'Unified School District' AND StatusType = 'Merged' / SELECT COUNT(*) FROM schools WHERE County = 'Orange' AND District = 'Elementary School District' AND StatusType = 'Merged'
SELECT schools.County, schools.School, schools.ClosedDate FROM schools WHERE schools.ClosedDate IS NOT NULL GROUP BY schools.County ORDER BY COUNT(schools.School) DESC LIMIT 1
SELECT schools.Street, schools.School FROM schools JOIN satscores ON schools.CDSCode = satscores.cds ORDER BY satscores.AvgScrMath DESC LIMIT 1 OFFSET 5
